-- Avocet Mining Boosts Gold Reserve Estimate at Burkina Faso Inata Project
-- B y   A m a n d a   J o r d a n
-- 2010-09-29T06:13:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-29/avocet-mining-boosts-gold-reserve-estimate-at-burkina-faso-inata-project.html
Avocet Mining Plc increased its
estimate of mineral reserves at the Inata project in Burkina
Faso by 25 percent to 1.08 million ounces of gold. The company
extended the mine life to 2018 at an average annual production
rate of 120,000 ounces.   To contact the reporter on this story:
